OL,3,CJersey lawyer handed 12-month practice
OL,4,Csuspension after drunken hit-and-run
OL,6,FA convicted Jersey lawyer has been
OL,7,Fsuspended from practising law for 12
OL,8,Fmonths after he crashed into an
OL,9,Foncoming vehicle whilst intoxicated.
OL,11,FAdvocate David Samuel Steenson was
OL,12,Finvolved in the incident on 16 May
OL,13,F2025, where, instead of stopping after
OL,14,Fthe accident, he left the scene and
OL,15,Fcontinued to drive his vehicle, which
OL,16,Fwas described as "significantly
OL,17,Fdamaged and unroadworthy" by jurats.
