OL,3,CJersey lawyer handed 12-month practice
OL,4,Csuspension after drunken hit-and-run
OL,6,FSteenson pleaded guilty to drink
OL,7,Fdriving, failing to stop, and
OL,8,Fdangerous driving, and was sentenced
OL,9,Fto seven months in prison.
OL,11,FNow, the decision was made by four
OL,12,Fjurats and the former Bailiff,
OL,13,FCommissioner Sir Timothy Le Cocq, to
OL,14,Fimpose the maximum practice suspension
OL,15,Fof 12 months.
