OL,3,CJersey lawyer handed 12-month practice
OL,4,Csuspension after drunken hit-and-run
OL,6,F"We feel that the appropriate penalty,
OL,7,Fwhich for a professional at his stage
OL,8,Fof career is hard indeed, is a
OL,9,Fsuspension from practice for the
OL,10,Fmaximum period possible, to commence
OL,11,Ffrom the date of his release from
OL,12,Fprison," the judgment reads.
OL,14,FIn their ruling, the jurats and the
OL,15,FCommissioner also took into account a
OL,16,Fprevious offence where Steenson had
OL,17,Fassaulted a taxi driver while drunk.
OL,19,FAt the time, Steenson was suspended
OL,20,Ffrom practising law in the island for
OL,21,Fthree months.
