OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F388A1769177571
OL,3,CJersey lawyer handed 12-month practice
OL,4,Csuspension after drunken hit-and-run
OL,6,F"It is rightly observed that the
OL,7,FRespondent's behaviour is not at all a
OL,8,Fmatter of dishonesty or breach of
OL,9,Fprofessional duty but rather behaviour
OL,10,Fin his private life which inevitably
OL,11,Fbrings the profession into disrepute,"
OL,12,Fthe judgement continued.
OL,14,F"It is a serious matter, and we do not
OL,15,Faccept Advocate Nicholls' submission
OL,16,F(Steenson's law partner) that there is
OL,17,Flittle, if anything, to be gained by a
OL,18,Ffurther sanction.
