OL,3,CJersey lawyer handed 12-month practice
OL,4,Csuspension after drunken hit-and-run
OL,6,F"It is right that members of the
OL,7,Fpublic know that if a member of the
OL,8,Flegal profession in Jersey, either in
OL,9,Ftheir professional or private lives,
OL,10,Fbehaves in such a manner, including
OL,11,Fthe commission of a criminal offence,
OL,12,Fthat brings the legal profession into
OL,13,Fdisrepute, they will meet with condign
OL,14,Fpunishment."
OL,16,FITV News has contacted Steenson
OL,17,FNicholls, the firm where Steenson
OL,18,Fworked as a senior named partner, but
OL,19,Fhas not had a response.
